Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
