Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩這麼多菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在減肥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 這些事不要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會兒有人要送貨來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貨送來後 先替我付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是電腦配件?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
