Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲 我們今晚去不去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CYBERIA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要發E-MAIL了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲 你要發給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會又是她吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 四方田千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你叫我們帶她到CYBERIA去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂跟那裡格格不入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她也不會再去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是突然想到一些怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些怪事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶中沒有的事就是不存在的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記億？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶中沒有那個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那人就根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲 你在說誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說那個人不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點下課就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這女孩是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來真是個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對這些很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快點嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽在等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那麼拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再猜一次 再猜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太郎不等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡滑了 再猜一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要離開這個公司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們竟要我做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要辭職 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要辭職 絕對要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶中沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就根本沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶只是一種記錄\N把它整理一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為所有人的記憶都沒有你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這不是你所希望的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再有人離奇的死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再有人受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會被人所憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡上會令人死亡的訊息已經全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不會再有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為如此 玲音也不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你最希望的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那個人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他從來就不存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有也不可能變成神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再胡思亂想了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已不存於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我是誰？ 人到底在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實網絡世界並存在現實世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡只是個傳送資料的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,資料是不會停留的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是不斷地傳送和交換罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,個人的記憶或是歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不知不覺中成為大家所共有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼龐大的記憶系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為人類能自行建構嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的只是連接網絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底連接著什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類有知道那個必要麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡聯繫何處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不知道也能繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的世界出著各種各樣的神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類認為這樣才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡這樣的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡也沒辦法 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該明白我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 玲音根本不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音只能看著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 其實玲音就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為神後會很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信會比一般人更快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事也不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就不會有人恨玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就不會有人討厭玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再從頭開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正又不是沒試過重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
