Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 下次我給你弄好喝的紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道一定會很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實記憶…不只是過去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它也關係到今天 甚至明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就依照你剛才所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你的心意去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但睡房的窗簾由我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老師 你說什麼就什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 這才是個好學生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 請等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過你嗎？ 有見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是我實習時教過的學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又不像 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是初次見面…的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？ 原來是初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是亞莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個普通的名字對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定將來還會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯 說不定會再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠和你在一起 永遠…
